text: This list includes Pictish kings since 312, kings have ruled the Picts since around 800 BC but the monarchs listed here are the kings and queens who have ruled the whole of Pictland or claimed to have ruled the whole of Pictland. == Kings of Pictland since 312 == * Vipoig 312-342 * Canutulachama 342-345 * Vuradech 345-347 * Gartnait 347-387 * Talorg 387-412 * Drest I 412-452 * Talorc 452-456 * Nechtan I 456-480 * Drest II 480-510 * Galan 510-522 * Drest III & Drest IV 522-530 & 522-531 * Gartnait II 531-537 * Cailtram 537-538 * Talorc II 538-549 * Drest V 549-550 * Galam 550-555 * Bridei I 555-584 * Gartnait III 584-595 * Nechtan II 595-616 * Cinioch 616-631 * Gartnait IV 631-635 * Bridei II 635-641 * Talorc III 641-653 * Talorgan 653-657 * Gartnait V 657-663 * Drest VI 663-672 * Bridei III 672-693 * Taran 693-697 * Bridei IV 697-706 * Nechtan III 706-724 (ferst ren) * Drest VII 724-726 (deposed bi Alpín) * Alpín 726-728 * Nechtan III 728-729 (seecond ren) * Onuist 729-761 & Talorcan 736-750 * Bridei V 761-763 * Ciniod 763-775 * Alpín II 775-778 * Talorc IV 778-782 * Drest VIII 782-783 * Talorc V 783-785 * Conall 785-789 * Caustantin 789-830 * Óengus 820-834 * Drest IX 834-837 & Talorc VI 834-837 * Éogan 837-839 * Uurad 839-842 * Bridei VI 842-843 * Ciniod II 843 * Bridei VII 843-845 * Drest X 845-848 == Kings of Pictland & Alba/Scotland == * Cináed mac Ailpín (843-858) * Domnall mac Ailpín (858-862) * Causantín mac Cináeda (862-877) == Disputed (kings of Pictland) == * Áed mac Cináeda (877-878) * Giric mac Dúngail (878-889) * Domnall mac Causantín (889-900) == Disputed (kings of Pictish Alba) == * Caisantín mac Áeda (900-943), abdicated.
